13
00:01:39,984 --> 00:01:43,774
<i>Soo Hyun can't write well, but he has a nice
voice. Soo Hyun is the man who made me love again.</i>

14
00:02:05,664 --> 00:02:10,464
<i>Soo Hyun, you are the man I love.</i>

15
00:02:22,854 --> 00:02:24,803
<i>I came to do a project.</i>

16
00:02:24,804 --> 00:02:28,253
<i>It's called the Choi Soo
Hyun rehabilitation project.</i>

17
00:02:28,254 --> 00:02:29,923
<i>You'll help me, won't you?</i>

18
00:02:29,924 --> 00:02:31,833
<i>Will you do it for me, please?</i>

19
00:02:31,834 --> 00:02:33,463
<i>Please eat a bit.</i>

20
00:02:33,464 --> 00:02:36,403
<i>Soo Hyun, you are responsible
