21
00:02:36,404 --> 00:02:38,664
<i>I love you, Soo Hyun.</i>

22
00:02:39,204 --> 00:02:44,684
<i>I'll never leave your side.</i>

23
00:02:47,454 --> 00:02:49,733
You're going to stop the experiment?

24
00:02:49,734 --> 00:02:50,913
Yes.

25
00:02:50,914 --> 00:02:53,413
