to do at this moment.

26
00:02:53,414 --> 00:02:54,573
I'm sorry.

27
00:02:54,574 --> 00:02:57,794
Last time, you said something
similar, why again?

28
00:02:59,464 --> 00:03:01,033
What's the problem?

29
00:03:01,034 --> 00:03:03,043
I'll solve all of them for you.

30
00:03:03,044 --> 00:03:06,053
